t is a major step not easily taken against a central bank as important and =
as much part of the Western networks as the central bank of Russia.=C2=A0</=
p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Russia=E2=80=99s foreign reserv=
es consist, in the first instance, of a set of accounting entries. But in a=
 crisis the accounting entries don=E2=80=99t matter at all. All that matter=
s are relationships, and if your relationships get bad enough then the mone=
y is as good as gone.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is a lot to dis=
like, or at least to be uncomfortable with, in this situation. There are th=
e Bitcoiners=E2=80=99 complaints: Financial transactions are a private matt=
