: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; =
border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> testifying about thos=
e crimes</a> in the New York federal criminal trial of his former underling=
, Roger Ng, who is accused of participating in those crimes with him:</p><b=
lockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Among his many admissions so far: fr=
equently lying to compliance officers, working on unapproved side deals, tr=
ying to get Goldman jobs for the Malaysian prime minister=E2=80=99s kids, a=
rranging hundreds of millions of dollars in bribes, pocketing more than $60=
 million in kickbacks for facilitating 1MDB=E2=80=99s bond deals, and getti=
ng paid $12 million by Goldman the first year he did so.</p></blockquote><p=
 style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also bigamy! Somehow he got bigamy into the mix!=
 Double bigamy!</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On Thursday, Le=
issner also confessed he was twice married to two women at the same time. H=
e said he =E2=80=9Cfaked=E2=80=9D a divorce decree in order to marry [Kimor=
a Lee] Simmons while still being married to then-wife, Judy Chan Leissner. =
He also told jurors he=E2=80=99d earlier falsified a divorce document in or=
der to marry Judy Chan in Hong Kong in about 2000.</p><p style=3D"margin: 1=
6px 0;">=E2=80=9CI photoshopped the divorce document,=E2=80=9D he said of h=
is 2014 marriage to Simmons, a fashion designer.=C2=A0</p></blockquote><p s=
tyle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">He faked two divorce documents! This is a man who =
just loves doing fraud.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I have to say, I ha=
ve no particular reason to think that Ng is=C2=A0<em>innocent</em>, but if =
I were on the jury I would acquit him out of sheer outrage. Even if he did =
crimes, Leissner was so much=C2=A0<em>worse=C2=A0</em>that it is absurd to =
